Second Department,

December, 1974

(December 5, 1974) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Stanley Ford, Petitioner, v. Leon J. Vincent, as Superintendent, Green Haven Correctional Facility, Respondent.

Application by petitioner for a writ of habeas corpus, denied. Cohalan, Acting P. J., Christ, Brennan and Munder, JJ., concur.
